		<title>Adding Chords to Your Bass Grooves &#8211; Bass Riff of The Week #13 (L#137)</title>
		<link>http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/chords/adding-chords-bass-grooves-riff-week.html</link>
		<comments>http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/chords/adding-chords-bass-grooves-riff-week.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 18 Nov 2014 13:06:32 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Geoff Chalmers]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Chords]]></category>
